We provide full turnkey solutions for commercial offices and buildings, warehouses and industrial facilities.

Call us now on 03 9238 4560 for a free consultation.

Our service promise: "ON TIME, ON BRIEF AND ON BUDGET."

Since 2003, we have established ourselves as a highly respected provider of end-to-end building and warehousing solutions, from small businesses through to major warehouse distribution centres. A1 Precision Solutions provide innovative, practical and cost-effective solutions for Australian and International private and publicly listed companies. We rely on building trustful relationships with our clients by always offering the best solution, not the most expensive solution. 

We project manage the solution from start to end, offering a single point of contact to reduce confusion and add accountability. 

OFFICES AND BUILDINGS
• Commercial and industrial interiors;
• Office fit-outs - including work stations, electrical and data, staff kitchens and bathrooms;
• Office extensions (including mezzanines);
• Building exterior refacing / facade refurbishments;
• Relocations, site closures and end-of-lease ‘Make Good’ services;
• Receptions, shopfitting and showrooms;
• Planned and reactive maintenance;
• Plans and permits.

WAREHOUSES AND INDUSTRIAL FACILITIES
• Warehouse layout, work flow optimization, operations consultancy;
• Australian made pallet racking, shelving and conveyor systems – sales and installation;
• Mezzanines and relocatable raised storage areas;
• Materials handling equipment (MHE);
• Pallet rack relocation and reconfiguration;
• OHS / Workplace Safety consultancy;
• Line marking, safety barriers and fencing;
• Rack protection systems;
• Australia Standards AS4084-2012 rack safety inspections and WorkSafe “PIN” notice corrections;
• Rack dismantle and buy-back options.

FABRICATION - In-house Construction Services
• Bespoke design;
• Fabrication.

